  "detailed_description": "<h1>ADD TO WISHLIST</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110490/extras/32f9bf274be5270cdfbc1ada1faa123d.poster.avif?t=1564244084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110490/extras/32f9bf274be5270cdfbc1ada1faa123d.webm?t=1564244084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110490/extras/32f9bf274be5270cdfbc1ada1faa123d.mp4?t=1564244084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>LAB Defence</strong> is a strategy stand-alone shooting game where a player is to kill all of the enemies attacking the Lab. <br><br>Chose the right time and strategy to kill all of your enemies one by one to complete the level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110490/extras/6b0b540c3eb48a9ecefd8d39370a6c8e.poster.avif?t=1564244084\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110490/extras/6b0b540c3eb48a9ecefd8d39370a6c8e.webm?t=1564244084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110490/extras/6b0b540c3eb48a9ecefd8d39370a6c8e.mp4?t=1564244084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LAB Defence is a small indie game featuring: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> different levels of enemies <br></li><li> ability to customize your robot <br></li><li> entertaining gameplay <br></li><li> minimalistic style</li></ul>",
